82
00:11:22,800 --> 00:11:24,800
What about this one?

83
00:11:24,800 --> 00:11:28,600
This is a special present for you. It's one of a kind.

84
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:32,500
I asked Sister Xia to record my match.

85
00:11:32,500 --> 00:11:34,200
Although you weren't there,

86
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,800
I thought you might want to see

87
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:39,700
how I did; watch when you're free.

88
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:43,000
Will you watch it?

89
00:11:48,900 --> 00:11:50,000
Coach.

90
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:52,100
Thank you.

91
00:11:52,100 --> 00:11:54,200
- How come you're here?
- I know, right?

92
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:56,200
I just got back, and she dragged me here

93
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:58,400
to support your business, Boss Jiang.

94
00:11:58,400 --> 00:12:00,300
We don't need you.

95
00:12:01,400 --> 00:12:02,700
What a bad temper,

96
00:12:02,700 --> 00:12:04,800
yet his business flourishes.

97
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:06,600
Thank you.

98
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:08,200
Thanks.

99
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:13,100
What place did you get?

100
