And your score?

101
00:12:16,300 --> 00:12:18,800
I had 6,347.

102
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,000
With more training,

103
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:25,600
I can surely reach 7,000.

104
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:27,200
