105
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:29,000
That's not cockiness.

106
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,400
I'm just stating a fact.

107
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:32,300
In front of others, I'm modest.

108
00:12:32,300 --> 00:12:34,200
But not in front of you.

109
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:36,400
I want to reassure you; that's all.

110
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:42,000
Why didn't you come watch the match?

111
00:12:42,800 --> 00:12:46,400
I called you that day, and you sounded upset.

112
00:12:49,800 --> 00:12:51,800
Let me answer this.

113
00:13:01,400 --> 00:13:02,600
Yes?

114
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:05,600
I can tell, you know.

115
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,800
What?

116
00:13:06,800 --> 00:13:08,500
You tell me what.

117
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:11,400
You are not a bad cook.

118
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:16,900
Are you trying to date Coach Luo?

119
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:23,000
Let me remind you, Duan Yu Cheng,

120
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:24,100
don't push your luck.

121
00:13:24,100 --> 00:13:26,200
What do you mean by that?

122
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:28,100
Explain clearly.

123
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:31,600
Coach Luo treats you well,

124
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:33,500
but you need to know the boundaries.

125
00:13:33,500 --> 00:13:35,600
Coach Luo and Coach Wu are together.

126
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:37,900
Do you think it's fun to interfere?

127
00:13:40,400 --> 00:13:43,100
Who said they're together?

128
00:13:43,100 --> 00:13:44,200
Do you have evidence?

129
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:46,500
I saw them holding hands.

130
00:13:50,800 --> 00:13:51,800
What are you doing?

131
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:53,200
We also held hands.

132
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:55,000
Are we together then?

133
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:57,600
Disgusting.

134
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:59,600
I won't explain to you.

135
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:02,000
I've done nothing wrong.

136
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:03,600
You're afraid of Coach Wu.

137
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:05,600
I'm not.

138
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:25,900
- Did Coach Wu call you just now?
- Yes.

139
00:14:26,800 --> 00:14:29,200
He's been dealing with some things lately.

140
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:32,000
He just called to tell me it's all right.

141
00:14:32,900 --> 00:14:37,400
So you didn't come to watch my match because of him?

142
00:14:39,800 --> 00:14:41,600
What is it?

143
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:46,000
You and Coach Wu

144
00:14:47,300 --> 00:14:50,000
aren't together, right?

145
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:53,800
You brat, you even dare ask that? Do you want a beating?

146
00:14:53,800 --> 00:14:57,700
If you two aren't together, then I can pursue you.

147
00:14:58,600 --> 00:15:01,200
But if you're in a relationship,

148
00:15:02,500 --> 00:15:04,200
things will be complicated.

149
00:15:04,200 --> 00:15:07,200
Because I don't want to get between others' relationships.

150
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:09,000
What are you talking about?

151
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:12,000
I-I don't need you to give me an answer now.

152
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:13,800
I-I can wait.

153
00:15:13,800 --> 00:15:15,900
I just want you to know,

154
00:15:15,900 --> 00:15:18,600
