172
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,600
Too close.

173
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:28,400
- Here?
- Yes, that's fine.

174
00:16:28,400 --> 00:16:30,400
That's good. Okay.

175
00:16:30,400 --> 00:16:31,400
Have you a clear view of my face?

176
00:16:31,400 --> 00:16:32,600
Yes. You look handsome.

177
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:34,000
All right.
- Come on.

