182
00:16:44,500 --> 00:16:46,600
- I'm over here.
- Okay. Okay.

183
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:48,200
I'm over here, Sister Xia.

184
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:50,600
Today is the first day of the National University Games.

185
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:53,000
It's the first day of the competition as well.

186
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:55,400
I will do my best!

187
00:16:55,400 --> 00:16:57,600
You're just rambling.

188
00:16:58,500 --> 00:16:59,600
I don't know what to say.

189
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:02,200
Either way, I will do my best.

190
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:03,600
- You can do it.
- I can do it!

191
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:08,400
♫  So maybe I was hasty ♫

192
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:14,200
♫ To feel misunderstood ♫

193
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:21,000
♫ It was not your job to save me ♫

194
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:23,400
♫ But still, I wished you would ♫

195
00:17:23,400 --> 00:17:25,000
Xiao Cheng!

196
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:29,200
- You got this!
- Go!

197
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:30,600
Go, Xiao Cheng!

198
00:17:30,600 --> 00:17:33,700
♫ Our love was interrupted ♫

199
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:37,200
♫ By all the things ♫

200
