201
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:43,400
Get up, Senior!

202
00:17:43,400 --> 00:17:46,800
♫ Now I know that what we had was something ♫

203
00:17:46,800 --> 00:17:50,200
♫ I wish that I had known it at the time ♫

204
00:17:50,200 --> 00:17:52,100
Sister Xia, don't record this.

205
00:17:52,100 --> 00:17:53,400
