222
00:19:03,400 --> 00:19:06,800
I thought you'd be devastated hearing that.

223
00:19:06,800 --> 00:19:08,800
Why should I?

224
00:19:08,800 --> 00:19:10,600
That regards them. I'm just me.

225
00:19:10,600 --> 00:19:13,200
It's only a matter of time for me to get in.

226
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:17,400
When Sister Xia said she wanted to quit earlier on,

227
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:19,900
I was worried about her.

228
00:19:20,800 --> 00:19:22,800
Jiang Tian is supportive of her.

229
00:19:22,800 --> 00:19:25,000
They've always had a stable relationship.

230
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:27,700
She's got nothing to worry about now.

231
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:33,800
So don't you think a healthy relationship

232
00:19:33,800 --> 00:19:37,400
is the best addition to one's journey forward?

233
00:19:40,700 --> 00:19:41,700
Coach.

234
00:19:41,700 --> 00:19:42,800
I...

235
00:19:42,800 --> 00:19:44,200
If you continue,

236
00:19:44,200 --> 00:19:46,600
I'll ban you from training three days.

237
00:19:48,200 --> 00:19:49,500
But...

238
00:19:53,600 --> 00:19:55,200
Fine.

239
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:03,300
Good.

240
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:05,900
Good.

241
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:08,500
Wonderful.

242
00:20:11,400 --> 00:20:14,000
Entering the national team is good news,

243
00:20:14,000 --> 00:20:15,600
very honorable.

244
00:20:15,600 --> 00:20:18,600
Train hard over there.

245
00:20:18,600 --> 00:20:21,000
Make our country proud.

246
00:20:28,300 --> 00:20:29,900
This scene...

247
00:20:30,800 --> 00:20:32,200
I didn't expect to see this.

248
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:33,100
I'm so happy for you.

249
00:20:33,100 --> 00:20:34,600
This is normal.

250
00:20:34,600 --> 00:20:37,000
Coach Gao is showing much self-restraint

251
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:39,000
since he shed a few tears of joy

252
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:41,600
instead of fainting from happiness.

253
00:20:41,600 --> 00:20:44,200
You're the pride of South Lake University.

254
00:20:45,300 --> 00:20:46,800
If I enter the national team,

255
00:20:46,800 --> 00:20:49,300
will you hug me with tears of joy, too?

256
00:21:01,100 --> 00:21:03,000
All the best.

257
00:21:05,400 --> 00:21:07,700
- Coach.
- Go train now.

258
00:21:13,800 --> 00:21:15,500
Congratulations.

259
00:21:18,600 --> 00:21:19,600
As his senior,

260
00:21:19,600 --> 00:21:21,600
you should invite all the high jump team

261
00:21:21,600 --> 00:21:23,400
to treat Mao Mao to a meal today

262
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:26,400
as a farewell and celebration.

263
00:21:26,400 --> 00:21:29,200
I'm not on the high jump team anymore.

264
00:21:29,200 --> 00:21:30,400
All right.

265
00:21:30,400 --> 00:21:32,600
We'll go without you then.

266
00:21:32,600 --> 00:21:34,800
No.

267
00:21:34,800 --> 00:21:36,700
I didn't say I wouldn't go.

268
00:21:36,700 --> 00:21:38,400
I'll come.

269
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:40,000
- What do you want to eat?
- I want...

270
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:41,800
Beef noodle soup will do.

271
00:21:41,800 --> 00:21:44,900
He entered the national team. It's not a big deal anyway.

272
00:21:49,200 --> 00:21:50,800
- Senior.
- What are you doing?

273
00:21:50,800 --> 00:21:52,600
I'll miss you a lot.

274
00:21:52,600 --> 00:21:53,600
All right, go away.

275
00:21:53,600 --> 00:21:54,800
It's not like we can no longer see each other.

276
00:21:54,800 --> 00:21:56,600
- Go away.
- Coach Luo.

277
00:21:56,600 --> 00:21:58,400
I'll miss you, too.

278
00:21:58,400 --> 00:22:00,100
All right.

279
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:04,000
I'll miss you, too.

280
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:08,000
I'll miss you, too, Mao Mao.

281
00:22:09,600 --> 00:22:11,000
All right, enough.

282
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:12,200
Stop...

283
00:22:17,400 --> 00:22:21,300
This time I have to praise the track and field team,

284
00:22:21,300 --> 00:22:23,000
especially for the shot put event.

285
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:26,800
